external_knowledge:
- Breweries can be metaphorically compared to wells;
- Beers in stock can be metaphorically compared to water in the well;
- A dry well represents a brewery with no beers in stock;
- The query ensures that even dry wells (breweries with no beers in stock) are included in the results.

sql:
SELECT MIN(num_beers)
FROM (
  SELECT COUNT(beer_id) AS num_beers
  FROM beers
  GROUP BY brewery_id
);

